Currently installation is tested only for Linux,
but should work for anny platform supported by GNURadio.

Requirements:
 * Gnuradio
 * gr-osmosdr

Install:
 Installation os not necesary, all should work as-is.
 Instalation for current user only can be done by command

make localinstall

all necesary files will be copied into directory ~/.grc_gnuradio/rstt.

Remember to set PYTHONPATH accordingly in your ~/.bash_profile:

export PYTHONPATH=${PYTHONPATH}:~/.grc_gnuradio

